{"tid":2354591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警亂拉FoodPanda速遞員偷外賣袋 並指控「以頭襲警」","createTime":"2021-01-05T14:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T16:54:55.000Z","uid":34147,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"82b174e808fd8322a781b024dd91a2f0b82e7d90","tid":2354591,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"警方執法手法再度惹起民憤。一名背上FoodPanda外賣袋的男子上周六在天水圍被數名軍裝員截查，軍裝警發現其銀包貼有「光時」貼紙，先恫嚇事主「而家有條《國安法》」，又質疑事主的外賣袋是「偷返嚟」，要求事主自證清白，最終將事主帶返警署。警方指，該男子涉盜竊及襲警被捕。有區議員說，事主扣留期間因情緒問題送院，至本周一獲准保釋。FoodPanda證實，片段中被捕者為其公司的自僱送遞員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Hll0JO-KMotDenfgDRpq1OdCuDA=/407x709/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RQFRJQ3YCZB7RB7HYW5PBGRVXY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHll0JO-KMotDenfgDRpq1OdCuDA%3D%2F407x709%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRQFRJQ3YCZB7RB7HYW5PBGRVXY.JPG&h=995b76cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該名軍裝警員貿疑事主是否FoodPanda袋的物主，更揚言：「我問緊你你咪答我囉，你唔答我我咪要拉你囉！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/spUguDzRH13R4RpBUE1pREwDtmE=/406x711/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D4MPXLHKI5DUJAQN2NQOM4UIBQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FspUguDzRH13R4RpBUE1pREwDtmE%3D%2F406x711%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD4MPXLHKI5DUJAQN2NQOM4UIBQ.JPG&h=f9f1ab74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n軍裝警着事主「影清楚」截查其銀包，但又發惡「你影還影，部機唔好越來越哄埋我度！」事主反駁：「而家係你哄埋我度喎阿Sir！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TjxMWm_fEIi6MmZ4V7iN6JgsCXw=/802x1394/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V2RQY3WFE5GXNKIGZ6KWDN6FAY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTjxMWm_fEIi6MmZ4V7iN6JgsCXw%3D%2F802x1394%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV2RQY3WFE5GXNKIGZ6KWDN6FAY.JPG&h=8f298cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手持事主身份證的軍裝警先問事主身份證號碼，並要求事主除下口罩。事主配合，惟警指「唔係好似樣喎」，又指事主銀包上疑張貼一張「光時」貼紙：「你知唔知而家有條《國安法》，你銀包呢個寫住咩嘢字啊？個銀包係咪你㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n索身份證要求除罩對樣 警：唔係好似樣喎！<br />\n網上流傳一條長約4分鐘的片段，數名軍裝警截查一名男子，相信由被截查的男事主拍攝。片段甫開首，一名戴眼鏡的軍裝即指事主不合作，警方將錄低整個過程，並指出事發時為本月2日晚上10時07分，地點為天水圍嘉湖銀座對出公園。<br />\n<br />\n片段顯示，手持事主身份證的軍裝警先問事主身份證號碼，又要求事主除下口罩；事主配合後，惟又被警指「唔係好似樣喎」，又問多次事主身份證號碼幾號。事主聲稱「發唔到音」，警即發惡：「我唔再同你玩落去！張身份證係咪你嘅？」<br />\n<br />\n01 就話貼哂, 蘋果就自己入去睇啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/D5IFYSPVNNGAPC6AOR2HKWUX5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FD5IFYSPVNNGAPC6AOR2HKWUX5Y%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=5897e7a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FD5IFYSPVNNGAPC6AOR2HKWUX5Y%2F&h=571a2511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/D5IFYSPVNNGAPC6AOR2HKWUX5Y/</a>"},{"pid":"f56f561540d714772d0f6db1e15c736888d0cd4c","tid":2354591,"uid":223816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"荒謬"},{"pid":"67f75d41aa9547aa822cf1c046cef87c90c79b48","tid":2354591,"uid":171088,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:52:26.000Z","msg":"呢隻狗既往績<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa62cf30f8f943036e470e7d824cfd7adddf4a0","tid":2354591,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:53:19.000Z","msg":"垃圾狗隻"},{"pid":"19567d9730b693d656f641e20fb6efba1211e88e","tid":2354591,"uid":161726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:53:47.000Z","m